PulteGroup Reports Loss, Expects to Be Profitable in ‘Back Half’ of 2011

-- B y   J o A n n e   N o r t o n
-- 
2011-04-28T10:35:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-28/pultegroup-reports-loss-expects-to-be-profitable-in-back-half-of-2011.html
PulteGroup Inc., the largest U.S.
homebuilder by revenue, said it expects to be profitable in the
“back half” of 2011.  Pulte today reported a first-quarter loss of 10 cents a
share. Analysts surveyed by Bloomberg had estimated a loss of 14
cents a share on average.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
JoAnne Norton at 
 jnorton@bloomberg.net  